  ["mucksnout runt"] = { 2, "lone kobold found on a cliff in Darkfeather Valley overlo...", "The Mucksnout Runt is a lone kobold found on a cliff in Darkfeather Valley overlooking Pinerock Basin in Highmountain, next to a treasure chest most notably containing the  [Delicate Roc Feather]. Players can kick the runt off of the cliff, sendin..." },
