  ["rohh the silent"] = { 2, "rare gnoll found in Galardell Valley", "Rohh the Silent is a rare gnoll found in Galardell Valley, Stonewatch Falls, or the Tower of Ilgalar in Redridge Mountains. He is on a 10.5-16 hour respawn timer and is stealthed by default, only coming out of hiding when an enemy gets close." },
