  ["rojmane"] = { 2, "wizened old quilboar shaman", "Rojmane was a wizened old quilboar shaman who lead a group of quilboar that attacked Brann Bronzebeard north of the Razorfen Downs. After Brann struck down several of his party, he called for parlay, and talked with Brann for some time of the hist..." },
